                <head>No. 755<lb/>
                    <hi rend="italic">Editorial Note</hi>
                </head>
                <p>In telegram 2468 from Tokyo, April 10, Ambassador <persName corresp="#p_AJM1"
                        >Allison</persName> commented on the impact of the Geneva Conference on
                    Japan. For text of this telegram, see <ref target="frus1952-54v16#pg_510">volume
